title: Stat Surprises + Burning Questions - Fantasy Football Podcast for 5/17
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason reveal big rankings surprises! Who stood out the most after projecting stats for every fantasy football relevant player? Plus, NFL News and tough decisions made while answering questions from the listener mailbag! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for May 17th, 2022.

Pre-order the 2022 UDK at UltimateDraftKit.com at the lowest price before June 1st -- Get instant access to Dynasty Startup & Rookie Rankings

(06:40) - Quick Question - Stat Surprises
(14:55) - NFL News (Jarvis Landry to Saints)
(23:10) - Mailbag
(23:35) - Travis Kelce or Mark Andrews?
(25:45) - Allen Robinson Outlook
(29:45) - Austin Ekeler or Ja’Marr Chase?
(31:40) - Ballers Fantasy Championships
(32:25) - Dolphins Running Backs
(36:40) - Amon-Ra St. Brown + 1.11 or Joe Mixon?
(40:10) - League of Record Keeper Rules
(42:00) - Producer Nickname Origins
